# Frontend quality (MedLens+)

## In-app health UI
- `product-ux` + `web-frontend` + `ui-accessibility` + `web-performance`
- References: `bencium-controlled-ux-designer`, `web-design-guidelines`, `react-best-practices`, `composition-patterns`, AccessLint

## Marketing / landing
- `product-ux` + `marketing-ui` + discovery stack (`technical-seo`, `content-seo`, `answer-engine-optimization`)
- `web-performance` before launch; `analytics-tagging` for GTM/pixels (no PHI)

## Authority
`safety-privacy` and `medical-safety.mdc` override all UI and tracking guidance.

